                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">You may need to Open US Bank Account Online from abroad to be able to send or receive money across borders, operate an international business, or invest in the US, and in that case, having a bank account in the US will make life much easier. A lot of individuals do not know that opening a bank account in the US is possible online, even when one is not in the United States. It is both convenient and it saves time, travelling costs, stress of going through paperwork physically.</p>
